Package: stringi
Version: 0.1-12
Date: 2013-11-17
Title: THE string processing package for R
Description: stringi is THE R package for correct, fast, and convenient
    string processing in each locale and any native character encoding.
    The use of ICU library gives R users a platform-independent and properly
    localized toolbox of functions with behavior known from other
    programming languages, like Java, Perl, Python, and PHP.
URL: http://stringi.rexamine.com/
BugReports: http://github.com/Rexamine/stringi/issues
ByteCompile: TRUE
Type: Package
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.0),
    base
SystemRequirements: ICU4C (>= 4.8)
License: LGPL-3 | file LICENSE
Suggests:
    testthat
